attributes.name: content-security-policy
attributes.content: default-src 'self' http://*.cnn.com:* https://*.cnn.com:* *.cnn.net:* *.turner.com:* *.ugdturner.com:* *.vgtf.net:*; script-src 'unsafe-inline' 'unsafe-eval' 'self' *; style-src 'unsafe-inline' 'self' *; frame-src 'self' *; object-src 'self' *; img-src 'self' *; media-src 'self' *; font-src 'self' *; connect-src 'self' *;
